{"tid":2054216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：不應利用學校作表達政治訴求場地","createTime":"2020-06-07T03:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T05:00:31.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"184a92b640f29f47fe0ca29f68d41346a32dcca5","tid":2054216,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"政務司長張建宗今日（7日）發表網誌，提到近日有人發起學生反對港區國安法立法的網上聯署，他批評有關舉動明顯是利用學生達到政治目的，認為社會各界要與學校合作，攜手阻止政治入侵校園。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗稱，任何人不應利用學校作為表達政治訴求的場地，更不應煽動學生，尤其是中小學生，在具爭議及正在發展的政治事件上表態或參與有關行動，社會各界要就此明確表示關注。   <br />\n<br />\n他又表示，留意到多名教育界代表和大專界校董會主席及校長等紛紛表態支持國安法立法，認為在社會複雜多變的環境下，正確教育下一代國家觀、歷史觀、民族情懷，以及正確價值觀的工作至為重要。"},{"pid":"d56ec6675a6b592a9ea0dd05f76dbd29c195b595","tid":2054216,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:48:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200607/s00001/1591499408728/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200607%2Fs00001%2F1591499408728%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUrHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=d5f042ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200607%2Fs00001%2F1591499408728%2F&h=76313df8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200607/s00001/1591499408728/</a>"},{"pid":"8657e047ad761b8a621cec590e3def6f75a714d3","tid":2054216,"uid":103156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:49:12.000Z","msg":"但可做反共基地！？"},{"pid":"351b11dff5947d6c9e33aff99f882a964182e99f","tid":2054216,"uid":132587,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"你地政府可以利用學校同教科書洗我地腦<br />\n我地宜家係學校講一句光復香港都唔得<br />\n無野呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3db0b9657ed0fa92a58a2b96ff2de703621a73f","tid":2054216,"uid":136431,"l